INSERT {
  GRAPH narr:Tx_20260521T120000Z {
    narr:Narrative_DirectIngestionAntiPattern narr:theme "CORRECTED: Direct historical transcript ingestion via AI summarization is a valid onboarding path — not an explicit anti-pattern. The anti-pattern framing was overplayed. Bulk summarization across a set is effective; the concern is unreviewed direct ingestion without summarization or topic analysis, not bulk ingestion per se." ;
      skos:note "2026-05-21 correction by Scarlet: The 'direct ingestion is an explicit anti-pattern' claim was wrong. Bulk ingestion via AI summarization was a deliberate, successful method Scarlet advised the customer's chief architect to use. The prior framing conflated unreviewed raw ingestion with summarization-mediated bulk ingestion." .
  }
}
