      skos:note "Three bulk ingestion methods ranked: (1) Full summarization across the set — what the customer's chief architect did, effective; (2) Per-transcript memory-by-memory ingestion — slow and overwhelming; (3) Target method — batched ingestion followed by a human reconciliation pass, or a hybrid of batched individual transcripts and cross-set topic summaries. Method 3 is best but depends on the reconciliation tool, which is not yet built." ;
      narr:aboutNode narr:Narrative_BulkIngestionValidMethod ;
